dr["Number12"] = PriceDiff + (Convert.ToDecimal(dr["DspExpUnitPrice"])); dr["ExpUnitPrice"] = PriceDiff + (Convert.ToDecimal(dr["DspExpUnitPrice"])); dr["DocExpUnitPrice"] = PriceDiff + (Convert.ToDecimal(dr["DspExpUnitPrice"])); dr["DocInListPrice"] = PriceDiff + (Convert.ToDecimal(dr["DspExpUnitPrice"])); dr["InExpUnitPrice"] = PriceDiff + (Convert.ToDecimal(dr["DspExpUnitPrice"])); dr["DocInExpUnitPrice"] = PriceDiff + (Convert.ToDecimal(dr["DspExpUnitPrice"])); dr["DspExpUnitPrice"] = PriceDiff + (Convert.ToDecimal(dr["DspExpUnitPrice"])); dr["DocDspExpUnitPrice"] = PriceDiff + (Convert.ToDecimal(dr["DspExpUnitPrice"])); dr["DocPotential"] = (PriceDiff + (Convert.ToDecimal(dr["DspExpUnitPrice"])))- (Convert.ToDecimal(dr["DiscountPercent"])/100) * (PriceDiff + (Convert.ToDecimal(dr["DspExpUnitPrice"])))* Convert.ToDecimal(dr["OrderQty"]); //dr["DspDiscount"] = 400;//PriceDiff + (Convert.ToDecimal(dr["DspExpUnitPrice"])) * (Convert.ToDecimal(dr["DiscountPercent"])/100); dr["DocDspDiscount"] = (Convert.ToDecimal(dr["DspExpUnitPrice"])) * (Convert.ToDecimal(dr["DiscountPercent"])/100); //MessageBox.Show(PriceDiff.ToString()) ; //QuoteDtl.DspDiscount dr["RowMod"] = "U"; dr.EndEdit();
adapterQuote.Update();
} }
adapterQuote.Dispose();
} catch (System.Exception ex) { ExceptionBox.Show(ex); } }
